      <h2>Availability</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Available for hire — AI Tooling & Software Engineering.</strong><br />
        Open to roles in AI implementation, workflow intelligence, internal tools, and frontend engineering.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:hey@dwaynemcyrus.com">hey@dwaynemcyrus.com</a><br />
        <strong>CV:</strong> <a href="/cv">View the CV</a>
      </p>
